      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 11 • Motivating Co-Workers",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Greg, Stan, and Donna work for Pack-It, a maker of trash bags and other consumer goods. After disappointing sales results, they discuss exiting the trash bag business. But a fresh new idea gives them hope for the future."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Greg: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Our sales were down again last quarter."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Donna: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We’ve been "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"working our tails off"
            },
            {
              "text":	" and our results are still lousy!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Greg: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Maybe we should exit the trash bag business — just "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"call it quits"
            },
            {
              "text":	"!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Stan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Come on. Let’s not "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"throw in the towel"
            },
            {
              "text":	" yet. "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"We’ve been down before, but we always come back fighting"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Donna: "
            },
            {
              "text": "But this time "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"private-label products"
            },
            {
              "text":	" are driving us out of business!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Stan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We’ve got a successful "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"track record"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Everybody knows that we offer quality trash bags."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Donna: "
            },
            {
              "text": "That’s true, but we can’t just "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"rest on our laurels"
            },
            {
              "text":	" forever."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Stan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Well, I have a new idea that’s going to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"turn around our business"
            },
            {
              "text":	". It’s a new line of trash bags that smell like fresh fruits, such as apples and peaches."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Greg: "
            },
            {
              "text": "That sounds like a great idea. I’m ready to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"roll up my sleeves"
            },
            {
              "text":	" and "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"get down to business"
            },
            {
              "text":	"!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Stan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I appreciate your "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"team spirit"
            },
            {
              "text":	"! Donna, are you "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"on board"
            },
            {
              "text":	" too?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Donna: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Sure. "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"Count me in"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Stan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Great. Let’s get everybody else in the Company excited about this plan, too. I’ll count on you two to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"rally the troops."
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
